{"word":"παραγράφω","slug":"παραγράφω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n77875\" key=\"paragra/fw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">παραγρᾰ´φ-ω</orth>, <sense id=\"n77875.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">write by the side</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πλησίον π.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">99</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"b\" id=\"n77875.1\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> mostly, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">add, subjoin</tr_>, esp. a clause to a law, contract, etc., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τί βεβούλευται περὶ τῶν σπονδῶν ἐν τῇ στήλῃ παραγράψαι</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">;</tr_> Id.<title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></title_> <pb n=\"1307\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:513\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">513</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:785a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">785a</biblScope> </bibl> (<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram> </gramGrp>); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. \"τῷ δεῖνι ἀποδοῦναι δεῖ\"</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg052.perseus-grc1:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">52.4</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑποκάτω π.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">add</tr_> particulars below, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0030.tlg003.perseus-grc1:30\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hyp.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eux.\">Eux.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">30</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. τὸ ὄνομα παρ᾽ ᾧ ἂν κείωνται αἱ συνθῆκαι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.1176.20</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"c\" id=\"n77875.2\" level=\"4\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">enter</tr_> a debt or liability against a person's name, c. acc. pers. et rei, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:488:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ POxy.\">POxy.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">488.32</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii/iii A. D.)</date>, <bibl n=\"Perseus:abo:pap,P.Oxy.:513:33\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">513.33</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii A. D.)</date>:—more freq. <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have entered against one,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PTeb.\">PTeb.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.189</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(ii B. C.)</date>, etc.: with personal subject, <cit TEIform=\"c