harge</tr_>, Test. ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:107\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.107</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n77875.12\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παραγεγραμμένος μὴ εἰσαγώγιμον εἶναι τὴν δίκην</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">having demurred to</tr_> the admissibility of the suit (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">παραγραφή</foreign> II. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1</biblScope> </bibl>), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg032.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">32.1</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. περί τινος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg038.perseus-grc1:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">38.1</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0010.tlg002.perseus-grc1:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Isoc.\">Isoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.2</biblScope> </bibl>: coupled with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπόμνυσθαι</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg047.perseus-grc1:39\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">47.39</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">45</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἑαυτὸν -όμενος μόνος ἀγωνίσασθαι τὴν δίκην ἐντολὰς οὐκ ἔχων</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">calling</tr_> himself <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">inadmissible</tr_> as pleader on the ground that he has no orders to plead alone, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0638.tlg003:2:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Philostr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ VS\">VS</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.32</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"5\" id=\"n77875.13\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">draw a line across, cancel</tr_>: metaph., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">efface</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ τιμᾶσθαι μετὰ τοῦτο πᾶσαν παρεγράψατο τὴν συμφοράν</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristid.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.246</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ J.\">J.</a></author> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁ θυμὸς τῇ ῥύμῃ τῆς ὀργῆς -γραφόμενος τὴν φύσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4091.tlg001:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Callistr.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Stat.\">Stat.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">v.l.</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">περι-</ref> </xr>):—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to be abolished</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰ φιλάνθρωπα παρεγράφη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0543.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:31:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S: